Entities:

User (id, username, email, passwordHash, role)

DeliveryRequest (id, customerId -> User, riderId -> User, pickupLocation (string), dropoffLocation, packageDetails, cost, status, timestamps)

Payment (id, deliveryId -> DeliveryRequest, customerId -> User, amount, status, transactionId)

RiderLocation (id, riderId -> User, lat, lng, updatedAt)

Relationships:

User (1) --- (M) DeliveryRequest (customer)

User (1) --- (M) DeliveryRequest (rider)

DeliveryRequest (1) --- (1) Payment

User (1) --- (1 latest) RiderLocation (or M for history)